{"tid":666220,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[專家入] 夏季滅蟑互助討論區","createTime":"2018-05-15T16:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T16:55:07.000Z","uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fa5a29aa44868e1a40c1a0e84833577451d11b","tid":666220,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢啫是來求救的 <br />\n<br />\n唔敢Search圖分品種，形容下曱甴：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>*一般街邊曱甴(深啡/深黑色，有啲個頭白白地，傳統曱甴樣)：</strong> <br />\n見到都嚇撚死，仲識飛。通常會經渠入屋。個殼比較硬，體型又一般較大，擊殺收屍會爛+爆漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n預防方法：定期用漂水消毒/物理遮擋閒置渠口<br />\n滅絕方法：超市買到既曱甴藥，放係經常出沒位置，都幾有效殺滅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新型曱甴A(棕啡色)</strong>：<br />\n呢隻體型細啲，殼比較軟，擊殺收屍較方便衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。常見於室內，用傳統曱甴藥好似冇乜效。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新型曱甴B(黑+啡+白，有紋)</strong>：<br />\n呢隻體型最細，殼極軟，身體水份重，擊殺後收屍最唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。呢隻又係室內常見，對食物極為敏感，但生命力頑強，難以根除。傳統曱甴藥效成疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以幫幫手分下品種，一齊傾下防治方法咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n圖片會令人情緒不安，希望大家高抬貴手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07b77c8bbaccd6399c7591253fda75285455296","tid":666220,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43d0843ca0c18d3b357c0538810941d0af8117da","tid":666220,"uid":105417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:30:41.000Z","msg":"淘寶買過一個德國藥廠嘅曱甴藥，係膏狀，一點點咁吱喺屋企啲角落位，好得。同超級市場買嘅好大分別。<br />\n<br />\n第一次見效係吱完第二朝見到有隻烏蠅僵硬地瞓咗喺地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed61394aab385b706783436904e682d2a6a52d72","tid":666220,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07b77c8bbaccd6399c7591253fda75285455296","tid":666220,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"是但一款都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"e6b236a631ea4c93b5b673fe9c708887f18a4607","tid":666220,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d0843ca0c18d3b357c0538810941d0af8117da","tid":666220,"uid":105417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:30:41.000Z","msg":"淘寶買過一個德國藥廠嘅曱甴藥，係膏狀，一點點咁吱喺屋企啲角落位，好得。同超級市場買嘅好大分別。<br />\n<br />\n第一次見效係吱完第二朝見到有隻烏蠅僵硬地瞓咗喺地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"同一點絕一樣？"},{"pid":"3ae1b4b34b95d9ac8096d756f8b538fc1cab55cd","tid":666220,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:45:14.000Z","msg":"用熱水淋即死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3941c7376cd05f428127f61857f85fe70b45ab22","tid":666220,"uid":105417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b236a631ea4c93b5b673fe9c708887f18a4607","tid":666220,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d0843ca0c18d3b357c0538810941d0af8117da","tid":666220,"uid":105417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:30:41.000Z","msg":"淘寶買過一個德國藥廠嘅曱甴藥，係膏狀，一點點咁吱喺屋企啲角落位，好得。同超級市場買嘅好大分別。<br />\n<br />\n第一次見效係吱完第二朝見到有隻烏蠅僵硬地瞓咗喺地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"同一點絕一樣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"未用過一點絕，係Bayer出的<br />\n香港唔知邊度揾到，一路都係淘寶買⋯⋯支嘢細細支，好似針筒咁款（無針）然後吱一點綠豆咁嘅size喺啲牆邊同角位。<br />\n<br />\n嗰時買話食咗藥仲會傳染俾其它曱甴，唔知堅定流，但上年用真完成個夏天都無曱甴。"}]}